	<div class="title">Where to Found Outposts</div>
	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">Outposts become cities (with luck), and thus you need to give some thought to where you will place them. Cities should be constructed in locations with plenty of food and production and with access to resources. When founding on land, it is often a good idea to build a city on a river or coastal hex. Cities constructed on hills gain a defensive bonus, making it harder for enemies to capture them. When founding on water, access to a land coast is likewise beneficial, while deep water represents a good place to expand to once the technology to move the city there is researched.</div>
